and here we are.

02:53.280 --> 02:54.479
That was it.
Yeah.

02:54.480 --> 02:57.045
[laughter and applause]

02:57.046 --> 02:58.545
I'm Lindsey.
I'm a violinist.

02:58.546 --> 03:00.512
I'm Nick,
and I'm an opera singer,

03:00.513 --> 03:02.579
and we're from New York.

03:02.580 --> 03:05.745
Growing up, my mother
had a Three Tenors album.

03:05.746 --> 03:07.479
At first I was like,
"Ah, why are you listening

03:07.480 --> 03:08.779
to all of this opera?"

03:08.780 --> 03:10.312
And then I started
singing along to it,

03:10.313 --> 03:11.712
and I fell in love with it.

03:11.713 --> 03:13.279
I said to myself,
that's what I want to do

03:13.280 --> 03:14.712
for the rest of my life.

03:14.713 --> 03:16.212
But in Staten Island,
New York,

03:16.213 --> 03:19.112
it's very hard to get a job
in the opera,

03:19.113 --> 03:23.279
so I had to pick up jobs
singing in restaurants

03:23.280 --> 03:25.245
and weddings
and whatever else I could.

03:25.246 --> 03:27.412
[gentle music]

03:27.413 --> 03:30.945
I started taking up
the violin around second grade.

03:30.946 --> 03:33.612
I loved classical music,
but I always felt

03:33.613 --> 03:36.579
like I didn't quite fit
in that world.

03:36.580 --> 03:38.379
But then when I met Nick,

03:38.380 --> 03:40.512
I felt like
I'd known him forever.

03:40.513 --> 03:41.779
Together we were like,

03:41.780 --> 03:44.112
"Oh, my gosh, we speak
the same language musically.

03:44.113 --> 03:46.412
This is incredible."

03:46.413 --> 03:48.579
We got married
and started to collaborate.

03:48.580 --> 03:50.079
This is the first time

03:50.080 --> 03:51.779
we're really putting
ourselves out there,

03:51.780 --> 03:54.345
and we're definitely trying
to make a career out of this.

03:54.346 --> 03:56.179
Winning "America's Got
Talent" would definitely

03:56.180 --> 03:58.712
change our lives,
and we cannot wait

03:58.713 --> 04:00.612
to show the world
what we do.

04:00.613 --> 04:01.779
Cannot wait.

04:01.780 --> 04:03.179
[cheers and applause]

04:03.180 --> 04:04.779
And why "AGT" this year?

04:04.780 --> 04:08.012
Because it's the greatest
show in the world.

04:08.013 --> 04:09.412
[cheers and applause]

04:09.413 --> 04:12.412
Okay, two minutes
to change your life forever.

04:12.413 --> 04:14.145
Thank you.
Yes.

04:14.146 --> 04:16.144
Good luck.
Okay, let's do this.

04:16.146 --> 04:17.612
[cheers and applause]

04:17.613 --> 04:19.480
[laughs]

04:25.113 --> 04:28.112
