Oh. Oh, gosh.
Oh, no.

05:01.646 --> 05:03.712
Are you serious?
What in the world?

05:03.713 --> 05:05.645
[knives clanging]

05:05.646 --> 05:09.179
♪ ♪

05:09.180 --> 05:12.179
Oh, my God.

05:12.180 --> 05:14.012
Oh, my gosh!

05:14.013 --> 05:17.445
♪ ♪

05:17.446 --> 05:19.412
[screams]

05:19.413 --> 05:20.845
[cheers and applause]

05:20.846 --> 05:23.845
[singing in Italian]

05:23.846 --> 05:27.245
♪ ♪

05:27.246 --> 05:29.612
Oh!

05:29.613 --> 05:36.146
♪ ♪

05:37.180 --> 05:39.645
Nobody try this at home.
Not at all.

05:39.646 --> 05:45.012
♪ ♪

05:45.013 --> 05:46.712
Uh-oh.

05:46.713 --> 05:49.712
[singing in Italian]

05:49.713 --> 05:56.279
♪ ♪

05:56.280 --> 05:58.279
Ohh!

05:58.280 --> 06:05.313
♪ ♪

06:10.180 --> 06:11.679
No.
And a blindfold!

06:11.680 --> 06:13.679
No!

06:13.680 --> 06:16.745
♪ ♪

06:16.746 --> 06:18.945
She's gonna light it on fire.
Oh, my God!

06:18.946 --> 06:21.046
[audience screams]

06:24.113 --> 06:26.113
[wild cheering]

06:29.180 --> 06:32.079
[Pat Benatar's
"Hit Me With Your Best Shot"]

06:32.080 --> 06:33.245
♪ ♪

06:33.246 --> 06:36.012
[laughs]

06:36.013 --> 06:40.479
♪ Well you're a real tough
cookie with a long history ♪

06:40.480 --> 06:41.979
♪ Of breaking little hearts
like the one in me ♪

06:41.980 --> 06:42.980
Oh, my God.

06:42.981 --> 06:45.279
My God,
I wasn't expecting that.

06:45.280 --> 06:46.979
Okay, Howie.
Ahh.

06:46.980 --> 06:50.279
We've seen knife throwers,
but not really with their feet.

06:50.280 --> 06:51.612
I am a self-taught
knife thrower.

06:51.613 --> 06:52.879
Wow.
[cheers and applause]

06:52.880 --> 06:55.345
Well, it's interesting,
it's dangerous, it's funny.

06:55.346 --> 06:58.112
You deserve to go further
than just tonight.

06:58.113 --> 07:00.312
Thank you so much.

07:00.313 --> 07:03.179
At what point in
the relationship did you say,

07:03.180 --> 07:04.745
"I've got an idea, honey"?

07:04.746 --> 07:06.612
