Howie?

07:47.580 --> 07:49.512
I'm gonna give you a yes.
I want to see you again.

07:49.513 --> 07:50.779
Thank you.

07:50.780 --> 07:53.245
Hell yeah.

07:53.246 --> 07:54.445
Thank you.

07:54.446 --> 07:57.445
Because of the singing,
I'm gonna say no.

07:57.446 --> 08:00.379
Aww.
[audience boos]

08:00.380 --> 08:02.812
You need three yeses.
You've already got two.

08:02.813 --> 08:05.212
So it's up to one lady.

08:05.213 --> 08:07.879
This is tough.
You know what, I will say that

08:07.880 --> 08:09.845
I actually really love your
voice and I don't actually

08:09.846 --> 08:12.412
think you should ever take
what you love

08:12.413 --> 08:15.079
and compromise it because
somebody doesn't like it.

08:15.080 --> 08:17.279
[cheers and applause]

08:17.280 --> 08:18.712
I think you should own it,

08:18.713 --> 08:20.945
and therefore, it's a yes.

08:20.946 --> 08:23.979
♪ Hit me with
your best shot ♪

08:23.980 --> 08:28.112
