08:35.313 --> 08:38.245
Will you throw a knife
at me with your feet?

08:38.246 --> 08:40.379
Yes, actually.

08:40.380 --> 08:43.044
Yeah!
Let's do it.

08:43.046 --> 08:45.246
[wild cheering]
Whoo!

08:47.713 --> 08:50.379
This is ridiculous.
Oh, my gosh.

08:50.380 --> 08:52.579
I really like you, yeah.
Thank you.

08:52.580 --> 08:54.212
This could go horrible wrong.

08:54.213 --> 08:56.312
Now, and this
will turn into a yes

08:56.313 --> 08:57.945
if you don't kill me, okay?

08:57.946 --> 08:59.379
I'm not gonna kill you.
Okay.

08:59.380 --> 09:01.412
That's my boss!
Take care of him!

09:01.413 --> 09:03.579
I love that she also
is self-taught.

09:03.580 --> 09:04.912
[laughs]

09:04.913 --> 09:06.345
Here we go!

09:06.346 --> 09:07.845
[cheers and applause]

09:07.846 --> 09:09.345
Oh, my God!

09:09.346 --> 09:12.579
[tense music]

09:12.580 --> 09:13.779
♪ ♪

09:13.780 --> 09:15.912
Ah!
One..

09:15.913 --> 09:17.679
two...

09:17.680 --> 09:18.745
three!

09:18.746 --> 09:20.912
♪ ♪

09:20.913 --> 09:22.780
[cheers and applause]

09:25.880 --> 09:28.145
Oh, my God.
Don't look.

09:28.146 --> 09:29.979
