09:34.680 --> 09:36.145
♪ Hit me with
your best shot ♪

09:36.146 --> 09:37.645
Thank you so much.
That's crazy.

09:37.646 --> 09:40.579
♪ Fire away ♪
It's four yeses.

09:40.580 --> 09:42.612
I'm just happy he's okay.

09:42.613 --> 09:44.445
I love you.

09:44.446 --> 09:46.612
You're out of your mind,
Simon.

09:46.613 --> 09:48.979
You're the only one
with a red buzzer.

09:48.980 --> 09:50.579
And then you said,
"Throw a knife at me."

09:50.580 --> 09:53.112
Oh, yeah.

09:53.113 --> 09:55.046
[laughter]

09:56.946 --> 09:59.179
What's your name, please?
Death.

09:59.180 --> 10:00.379
[cheering and gasps]

10:00.380 --> 10:03.379
You came to slay,
and I am deceased.

10:03.380 --> 10:05.245
