10:05.246 --> 10:07.779
You are getting on
my nerves right now.

10:07.780 --> 10:10.079
Oh, my God.
I'm too scared.

10:10.080 --> 10:12.445
That was
a spectacular performance.

10:12.446 --> 10:14.545
You made a believer
out of all of us.

10:14.546 --> 10:17.945
You are fantastic.
Really fantastic.

10:17.946 --> 10:19.612
Hit the Golden Buzzer!

10:19.613 --> 10:22.346
[cheers and applause]

10:26.313 --> 10:26.346
.

10:27.913 --> 10:28.613
What's your favorite food?

10:28.446 --> 10:28.613
Oatmeal.

10:29.546 --> 10:30.812
Oatmeal?

10:30.813 --> 10:33.345
♪ Food, glorious food ♪

10:33.346 --> 10:35.480
Dinner tonight.
That's all I'm thinking about.

10:37.046 --> 10:38.345
Egg with asparagus,

10:38.346 --> 10:39.745
Scottish smoked salmon
with lobster.

10:39.746 --> 10:41.945
Did Simon arrange this?
Yes.

10:41.946 --> 10:43.912
