Yes, of course, sir.

10:43.913 --> 10:46.579
What's a petit four?
It's a very small cake.

10:46.580 --> 10:48.779
No, you're supposed to say,
"It's for eating."

10:48.780 --> 10:50.379
Ohh.
I'm sorry, sir.

10:50.380 --> 10:52.079
I miss the American humor.

10:52.080 --> 10:54.279
[laughs]

10:54.280 --> 10:56.545
My favorite food,
mac and cheese.

10:56.546 --> 10:58.979
Chicken finger.
Chicken wing.

