Mm, yes.

11:33.446 --> 11:34.512
Whoo!

11:34.513 --> 11:35.912
We both have so much fun,

11:35.913 --> 11:38.179
but we've been practicing
so hard.

11:38.180 --> 11:40.012
The song we're
performing to tonight

11:40.013 --> 11:42.545
