gonna do here for us?

12:34.646 --> 12:36.279
We're gonna dance.

12:36.280 --> 12:38.012
Are you guys related,
brother/sister?

12:38.013 --> 12:39.445
No.

12:39.446 --> 12:41.112
Oh, so how long have you guys
been dancing together?

12:41.113 --> 12:42.912
For about, like, five years.
Yeah.

12:42.913 --> 12:44.545
So what type
of dance do you do?

12:44.546 --> 12:46.279
Contemporary.

12:46.280 --> 12:47.812
I love that they keep
looking at each other.

12:47.813 --> 12:49.345
It's so cute.
Good luck.

12:49.346 --> 12:50.812
Let's see what you got.

12:50.813 --> 12:52.512
Does anybody like
contemporary dance?

12:52.513 --> 12:53.945
Yes.
Just out of interest.

12:53.946 --> 12:55.579
Like who?
Me.

12:55.580 --> 12:57.512
Anyone else?
Everyone.

12:57.513 --> 12:59.212
Who?
In the world.

