oh, no, this is pretend.

53:00.313 --> 53:02.245
This is virtual reality,

53:02.246 --> 53:03.912
but the virtual
kept going away,

53:03.913 --> 53:05.612
and it was really my reality,

53:05.613 --> 53:09.479
and I've never seen something
that is so enveloping,

53:09.480 --> 53:11.279
and I'm a proponent
of mental health

53:11.280 --> 53:12.479
and removing the stigma.

53:12.480 --> 53:13.945
Wow.
That was amazing.

53:13.946 --> 53:15.579
[cheers and applause]

53:15.580 --> 53:17.612
Gabrielle.
It was just awesome

53:17.613 --> 53:19.579
watching Howie
overcome his fears.

53:19.580 --> 53:22.912
I was on the edge of my seat.
It was exhilarating.

53:22.913 --> 53:24.479
Amazing job.
Thank you, guys.

53:24.480 --> 53:26.779
Thank you.
Julianne.

53:26.780 --> 53:29.245
My heart was racing for you.

53:29.246 --> 53:31.179
That was stuff I've
never actually seen before,

53:31.180 --> 53:34.045
and honestly
that was so much fun.

53:34.046 --> 53:36.012
I think people
are gonna love this,

53:36.013 --> 53:38.845
so thank you for coming to
"America's Got Talent."

53:38.846 --> 53:40.879
Thank you.
[cheers and applause]

53:40.880 --> 53:42.345
Simon?

53:42.346 --> 53:44.679
Well, you know what,
what was cool about this

53:44.680 --> 53:47.812
