what you were seeing,

53:47.813 --> 53:49.245
which is normally--
You could see it?

53:49.246 --> 53:50.912
Yeah, yeah.
They could.

53:50.913 --> 53:52.245
It's amazing,
and it is entertaining.

53:52.246 --> 53:56.012
Plus, it was even better
seeing Howie look silly.

53:56.013 --> 53:57.612
[laughter]

53:57.613 --> 53:59.745
It was different,
and I liked it.

53:59.746 --> 54:01.479
Well done.
Thank you.

54:01.480 --> 54:03.845
So let's vote.
Go ahead, Simon.

54:03.846 --> 54:06.312
I'm gonna say yes.
Julianne.

54:06.313 --> 54:08.712
Absolutely yes for me.
Thank you.

54:08.713 --> 54:11.512
Gabrielle.
That's a yes for me too.

54:11.513 --> 54:14.112
Thank you.
For me, it was fantastic,

54:14.113 --> 54:16.245
and for me alone,
four yeses.

54:16.246 --> 54:18.645
♪ Standing
in the hall of fame ♪

54:18.646 --> 54:20.645
♪ ♪

54:20.646 --> 54:22.012
♪ And the world's gonna
know your name ♪

54:22.013 --> 54:24.345
Thank you.

54:24.346 --> 54:25.512
♪ ♪

54:25.513 --> 54:27.045
How do you feel right now?

54:27.046 --> 54:28.812
Right now...
I still can't believe it.

54:28.813 --> 54:30.479
Yeah.
That was completely crazy.

54:30.480 --> 54:31.645
Could you see
through my goggles?

54:31.646 --> 54:33.345
We could see
what you were doing.

54:33.346 --> 54:35.079
No, it was cool
because they cut away

54:35.080 --> 54:36.712
to all these different
camera angles.

54:36.713 --> 54:37.979
It was good.

54:37.980 --> 54:40.280
♪ Standing in
the hall of fame ♪

54:43.313 --> 54:43.346
.

54:44.713 --> 54:44.880
[laughter]

54:46.746 --> 54:48.212
Oh, my gosh,
this is so amazing.

54:48.213 --> 54:50.412
I can't believe we're here.

54:50.413 --> 54:53.245
Wow!
I like your outfit!

54:53.246 --> 54:54.712
Thank you.

54:54.713 --> 54:57.745
Being here is just
a dream come true.

54:57.746 --> 54:59.545
Whoa.

54:59.546 --> 55:00.945
Do you feel nervous?

55:00.946 --> 55:02.479
Let's just hold my hand.

55:02.480 --> 55:05.345
We're excited for you.
Hope you do good.

55:05.346 --> 55:07.345
There's a huge crowd.

55:07.346 --> 55:10.145
This is one of the biggest
stages in the world.

55:10.146 --> 55:12.145
Oh, it is the biggest
stage in the world.

55:12.146 --> 55:14.912
Wow.
You see?

55:14.913 --> 55:16.745
This your good luck charm?
Mm-hmm.

55:16.746 --> 55:18.479
Oh.
What's his name?

55:18.480 --> 55:20.379
Uni.
Uni.

55:20.380 --> 55:22.412
Okay, listen,
let's go out there

55:22.413 --> 55:23.979
and show 'em what you got.

55:23.980 --> 55:25.479
High five.
All right.

55:25.480 --> 55:27.812
Go out there
and give it to 'em.

55:27.813 --> 55:30.479
[cheers and applause]

55:30.480 --> 55:31.979
Aww.
Oh.

55:31.980 --> 55:35.312
Hi!

55:35.313 --> 55:37.045
Hello.
Hello.

55:37.046 --> 55:38.979
Hi, sweetheart.
What's your name?

55:38.980 --> 55:40.445
Emanne.
Emanne?

55:40.446 --> 55:42.045
Yeah.
Where are you from?

55:42.046 --> 55:43.779
From North Port, Florida.

55:43.780 --> 55:45.112
Right on.
Yeah.

55:45.113 --> 55:46.979
And how old are you?
I'm ten.

55:46.980 --> 55:48.412
You're ten?
Yeah.

55:48.413 --> 55:51.345
[giggles]
I'm so nervous.

55:51.346 --> 55:52.879
Are you here
with your parents?

55:52.880 --> 55:55.012
Uh, yeah, I'm here with
my parents and my brothers.

55:55.013 --> 55:56.212
And your brothers.
Yeah.

55:56.213 --> 55:57.779
Are you the only girl
in your family?

55:57.780 --> 56:00.379
